{"tid":1418701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊入黎，我地連登一條心，支持勇武，絕不分化！","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:28:18.000Z","uid":3716,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2aec19b18075642e717304ece04ad35da9311b8","tid":1418701,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:53:40.000Z","msg":"Laser同火攻對象需要留意下<br />\n其他果啲老作誇大全部去含撚<br />\n你班p仔想藉此洗底反前線係冇可能<br />\n我地連登仔女係唔會比你班打手分化<br />\n冇勇武呢場運動一早收皮<br />\n你班冷氣撚一早比人斬撚死射撚死<br />\n同埋唔好再反光復香港呢個口號你班仆街<br />\n呢個係我地嘅信念同精神支柱<br />\n冇呢個口號就冇我地<br />\n相信前線嘅根本全都係港獨撚<br />\n後面嘅亦都聽唔到<br />\n改黎把撚<br />\n（和理非集合另計）<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n連登人一齊入黎集氣<br />\n對抗分化！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27c130ea6acf2f700d9c602551ee635db373ccc","tid":1418701,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1f0ca14635f684cf72f6c7546787bbd309b2bc","tid":1418701,"uid":285409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:02:27.000Z","msg":"呢幾日可否麻煩文宣多少少出黎做勢 入黎支持下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418595</a>"},{"pid":"e8003ee194b59fced42583abfc399ce87f69cdbc","tid":1418701,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a088bddf3abb672691f1668e570941ff5920b4","tid":1418701,"uid":292154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:14:19.000Z","msg":"支持勇武<br />\n我愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便推post<br />\n【玩火】正與反及檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417724</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee065769fa8f1ea89107203b791c9d702b4a47b0